data.description: Step into your new home in East Chula Vista, where the charm of the neighborhood meets urban comfort. This 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom house is perfect for a family looking to settle in a friendly community. Walk into a cozy setup that seamlessly connects the family, living, and kitchen areas on the main floor. The low-maintenance yard provides ample space for entertaining. Upstairs, you'll find four bedrooms, offering both privacy and abundant space for the entire family. This home also features a 2-car garage attached, as well as plenty of street parking. The community includes a low HOA with amenities such as an Olympic-style swimming pool, beach volleyball court, and a sprawling playground. Enjoy the convenience of a quick walk over the bridge to the Otay Ranch Town Center, where you'll find a variety of dining and shopping options to suit your preferences. Tastefully updated, this home is move-in ready.
